## Layout and config (Jekyll / GitHub Pages)

The `docs/` site is built with Jekyll. Respect the following when creating or editing docs.

### `_config.yml`

- Lives at `docs/_config.yml`. Defines site-wide settings (e.g. `title`, `description`).
- **Do not** remove or rename required keys. Add or change only specific values (e.g. title/description) unless you intend a structural change.
- Keep the file valid YAML (no stray colons in values, consistent indentation).

**Exact current content (`docs/_config.yml`):**

```yaml
title: NRS Branch Closure - 2026
description: NRS branch closure and opening analysis documentation
```

### `_layouts/`

- Layout templates live in `docs/_layouts/`. They wrap page content with HTML and shared styles.
- **Do not** remove or relocate `_layouts/`; Jekyll expects it at the root of the source directory (`docs/`).

### `default.html`

- The default layout is `docs/_layouts/default.html`. It provides the outer HTML, `<head>`, and injects `{{ content }}` where the page body goes.
- **When adding new docs:** Use front matter `layout: default` so the page uses this layout and the site’s styles/navigation pattern.
- **When editing the layout:** Preserve the `{{ content }}` tag so page content still appears. Avoid removing or changing the existing `<style>` block unless you are intentionally updating site-wide styles.

**Exact current content (`docs/_layouts/default.html`):**

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ page.title | default: site.title }}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ '/css/site.css' | relative_url }}">
  <!-- Hypothesis -->
  <script async src="https://hypothes.is/embed.js"></script>
  <style>
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; max-width: 1024px; margin: 0 0 0 0; padding: 2rem 1rem; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: border-box; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #333; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    li { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    a { color: #012169; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .desc { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
    p { margin: 0.5rem 0; }
    pre, code { font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; border-radius: 3px; }
    pre { padding: 0.75rem; overflow-x: auto; }
    pre code { padding: 0; background: none; }
    blockquote { margin: 0.5rem 0; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; color: #555; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  {{ content }}
</body>
</html>
```

**Example front matter for a new doc page:**

```yaml
---
layout: default
title: Your Page Title — NRS Branch Closure
---
```
